      <description>Win10配置Scala和Spark</description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<h1 id="一准备">一、准备</h1>
<p>基本信息</p>
<ul>
<li>操作系统: Windows10</li>
<li>jdk版本: 1.8</li>
<li>Hadoop版本: 2.9.2<img loading="lazy" src="../Win10%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aeScala%e5%92%8cSpark/java.png" alt="java"  />
</li>
</ul>
<p>下载并解压</p>
<ul>
<li>Scala： <a href="https://www.scala-lang.org/download/">官网</a> 或者 <a href="https://downloads.lightbend.com/scala/2.13.2/scala-2.13.2.zip">scala-2.13.2.zip</a></li>
<li>Spark：<a href="http://spark.apache.org/downloads.html">官网</a> 或者 <a href="https://mirror.bit.edu.cn/apache/spark/spark-3.0.0-preview2/spark-3.0.0-preview2-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz">spark-3.0.0-preview2-bin-hadoop2.7.tgz</a></li>
</ul>
<h1 id="二scala">二、Scala</h1>
<h2 id="配置">配置</h2>
<ul>
<li>
<p>新建系统变量 <code>SCALA_HOME</code> 至所在目录，如 <code>D:\environment\scala-2.13.2</code></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="../Win10%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aeScala%e5%92%8cSpark/scala_home.png" alt="scala_home"  />
</p>
</li>
<li>
<p>在 <code>path</code> 中添加 <code>%SCALA_HOME%\bin</code></p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="../Win10%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aeScala%e5%92%8cSpark/scala_bin.png" alt="scala_bin"  />
</p>
</li>
</ul>
<h2 id="测试">测试</h2>
<p>启动命令行，运行 <code>scala -version</code> ，出现以下结果说明成功</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="../Win10%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aeScala%e5%92%8cSpark/scala_version.png" alt="scala_version"  />
</p>
<h1 id="三spark">三、Spark</h1>
<p>启动命令行，配置环境变量或者<code>cd</code> 至 Spark的 <code>bin</code> 目录下，运行 <code>spark-shell</code> 出现以下结果说明成功。若出现错误，则依据错误提示安装Python或者Hadoop。</p>
<p><img loading="lazy" src="../Win10%e9%85%8d%e7%bd%aeScala%e5%92%8cSpark/spark.png" alt="spark"  />
</p>
]]></content:encoded>
